CREATE TABLE AggTempExtremes (
    date Date,
    max_temp_F FLOAT,
    min_temp_F FLOAT
);
GO

-- Insert data into AggTempExtremes
INSERT INTO AggTempExtremes (
    date, 
    max_temp_F, 
    min_temp_F
)
SELECT 
    date,
    max_temp_F,
    min_temp_F
FROM 
    ExternalAggTempExtremes
GO
